;

BIOMOLECULE: 1, 2

THIS ENTRY CONTAINS THE CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC ASYMMETRIC UNIT
WHICH CONSISTS OF 2 BIOLOGICAL UNITS. 

THE FIRST BIOLOGICAL UNIT CONTAINS PROTEIN CHAINS A+B AND 
HETGROUPS CIT 601 AND 602, GOL 701 AND 702 AND 
HOH RESIDUES NOT STARTING WITH A PREFIX 5000.

THE SECOND BIOLOGICAL UNIT CONTAINS PROTEIN CHAINS C+D AND
HETGROUPS CIT 5601 AND 5602, GOL 5701 AND 5702 AND 
HOH RESIDUES STARTING WITH A PREFIX 5000.
;
# 
